{"aid": "igkp02qb4yl1zp", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 3, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i73gb4scbtd", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-10T15:33:06Z", "content": "<p></p><ol><li>3.3中说到的<strong>“中断是持续的&#xff0c;对应用程序是透明的”</strong>这个应该怎么理解呢&#xff1f;</li><li>为什么说“中断”是<strong>异步</strong>的呢&#xff1f;</li></ol>", "subject": "关于中断的理解"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": ["hcrrjuyequh4bt"], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634788563, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-10T15:44:38Z", "id": "i73gxrznxha45z", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-10T15:44:38Z", "content": "1 中断会持续产生&#xff08;比如时钟中断&#xff09;。但如果应用程序不去&#34;关注&#34;时钟&#xff0c;是意识不到有时钟中断的。这就是通过操作系统的管理使得中断对应用程序“透明”。\n\n2. 我理中断的异步性实际上是指外设何时产生中断是不确定的这种特征。", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "i6tx0nskPKr", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-12T10:22:06Z", "id": "i760apdpozn7ly", "updated": "2015-03-12T10:22:06Z", "subject": "<p>中断是因为来自I/O的设备的信号&#xff0c;可以与现在执行进程无关&#xff0c;也可以并不是因为正在执行的进程所发出的信号&#xff0c;所以说是异步的</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 79, "created": "2015-03-10T15:33:06Z", "id": "i73gixrgsjn5n3", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 66, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["quiz3"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i73gb4scbtd", "when": "2015-03-10T15:33:06Z", "data": "i73gixrjtm75n4", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "when": "2015-03-10T15:44:38Z", "data": "i73gxs0le4460", "to": "i73gixrgs